      <prop type="x-chinese-ref">詩經·國風·鄘風·005.1</prop>
      <prop type="x-translation-ref">鶉之奔奔.1</prop>
      <tuv xml:lang="zh-Hant">
        <seg>鶉之奔奔，鵲之彊彊，人之無良，我以為兄。</seg>
      </tuv>
      <tuv xml:lang="en">
        <seg>Boldly faithful in their pairings are quails;
Vigorously so are magpies.
This man is all vicious,
And I consider him my brother!</seg>
      </tuv>
    </tu>
